race.comment: ALFA LILY (13) loves this track and trip with two wins and a placing from four attempts and will be high on confidence following that last-start victory here. Gets in on the minimum weight and should be going very close again. RESURRECTED (1) had put four wins together on the bounce before not measuring up in the Murwillumbah Cup before the spell. Revved up for this with a recent trial and a strong showing while fresh would not surprise. MARAGICAL (9) will find this easier than what she contested before the break and can run a big race while fresh. NIGHTCAPPED (10) rounds out the selections in an open contest.
